{"name":"Agile","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-content/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 36\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>+1 AC bonus when unarmoured and unencumbered (small shield allowed).</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"scout","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679252841676,"modifiedTime":1681579325695,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"lWxXUzGEYHEkPqG8","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
{"name":"Track","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-content/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 112\">\n<div class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>To stalk prey, tracing physical signs and discerning subtle clues. A scout can track at the below suggested probabilities:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Wilderness: A base 7-in-12 chance to find, identify, and follow fresh tracks outdoors or in natural caverns.</li>\n<li>Non-Wilderness: A base 9-in-12 chance to discern tracks in a dungeon, castle, city street, or like setting.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Furthermore, the scout can identify in general terms the species tracked if it is a known animal type (e.g., a large feline, a heavy bovine, a small canine). N.B.: The referee may adjust the chance-in-twelve to track based on prevailing circumstances.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"scout","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Q7eHkvfQRl80TQBF"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679252890133,"modifiedTime":1681579325696,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"mncTjTmNpOPSYirC","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
{"name":"Hide","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-content/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 37\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>To vanish into shadows, camouflage oneself, or flatten one&rsquo;s body to a seemingly impossible degree&mdash;all whilst remaining still as a statue. Only the slightest movement is permissible (e.g., unsheathing a blade, opening a pouch). Hiding is impossible in direct sunlight, or if the scout is observed.</p>\n<p>Scouts also practice almost all thievish skills. The following abilities improve as the scout advances in levels of experience, comparable to the thief.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>[<strong>Table 16: Progressive Thief Abilities</strong> -- see <strong>Player's Manual</strong>, p.37]</p>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"scout","roll":"d12","rollType":"below","rollTarget":5,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679253228973,"modifiedTime":1681579325696,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"qWLF8s99f5CKEMC0","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
